Sandra Nelson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sandra_Nelson 0 Sandra Nelson Winkler (born December 29, 1964), more commonly credited as Sandra Nelson, is an American actress. She was born in Madison, Wisconsin, and is best known for her role as Phyllis Summers on The Young and the Restless from 1997 to 1998. Nelson played a role as Aliyah Farran in The Wolf of Wall Street. Sandra_Nelson_Winkler ( born December_29_,_1964 ) , more_commonly credited as Sandra_Nelson , is an_American_actress .
